                <h1 class="domdom">10</h1>

                <h1>Film: <a href="/on/film/316">African In Motion: As Old As My Tongue + Live Music! (2007)</a></h1>

                <h2>10 Dec 2008, 7 p.m.</h2>

                <p>Film: As Old as My Tongue about the remarkable story of the oldest singer in the world, Zanzibari legend Bi Kidude. Followed by live Music from Sierra leone!

</p>

                <p class="viewlink"><a href="/on/film/316">Read More &raquo;</a></p>

